name: Artificial Victorian dreams on clods - Serie 1 - Gift for collectors

metadata.description:
**This dream is claimable free of charge by the first 9 who collect at least 3 dreams from Artificial Victorian dreams on clods - series 1**

Amid the clods, three towers rise majestically. One of them is a Victorian lady soaring with grace and pride, a living symbol of the strength that women embody in society. The dream celebrates the strength, wisdom and courage of women who face the world with pride and determination, illuminating dark ways, breaking patterns and traditions.
metadata.name: The three towers #1/9
